  "author": "山高县",
  "content": "<p>东京皇居的建成时间是1888年，只比颐和园早七年。也就是说，在老佛爷修院子的时候，天闹黑卡也在盖宫殿。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f5bb33fd361f9e5cff5408d9dae1d64_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"700\" data-rawheight=\"479\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-00324cad9e45709f262206c31a77c03e_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"700\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-5f5bb33fd361f9e5cff5408d9dae1d64_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;700&#39; height=&#39;479&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"700\" data-rawheight=\"479\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-00324cad9e45709f262206c31a77c03e_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"700\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-5f5bb33fd361f9e5cff5408d9dae1d64_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-5f5bb33fd361f9e5cff5408d9dae1d64_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>谁说天闹黑卡不修园子了？</figcaption></figure><p>而每块红砖都从英国买来的江田岛海军兵学校大楼，建成时间是1893年。</p><p>国贼海军马鹿在霞关的老巢，建成时间更是已经火烧眉毛的1894年。同期完工的，还有法务省国贼和大审院国贼的大楼。。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c175f4f97ff5f879d6f53f80460c25bc_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"802\" data-rawheight=\"339\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ebc32b50ee63f79c7c44540eefbcf4d_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"802\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c175f4f97ff5f879d6f53f80460c25bc_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;802&#39; height=&#39;339&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"802\" data-rawheight=\"339\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-3ebc32b50ee63f79c7c44540eefbcf4d_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"802\" data-original=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-c175f4f97ff5f879d6f53f80460c25bc_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-c175f4f97ff5f879d6f53f80460c25bc_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>海军马鹿浪费国民血税，简直是清国卧底</figcaption></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-84ee5465f386e4692d4903300cd83e30_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"656\" data-rawheight=\"465\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bddd63d1cd1a9fddf38c3c1b9a7514f3_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"656\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-84ee5465f386e4692d4903300cd83e30_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;656&#39; height=&#39;465&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"656\" data-rawheight=\"465\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-bddd63d1cd1a9fddf38c3c1b9a7514f3_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"656\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-84ee5465f386e4692d4903300cd83e30_r.jpg\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-84ee5465f386e4692d4903300cd83e30_hd.jpg\"/><figcaption>海军马鹿平时骄奢淫逸，战时贪天之功</figcaption></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-f406e6b7c6499c2cc1f2783e1794cc59_hd.jpg\" data-rawwidth=\"513\" data-rawheight=\"300\" data-size=\"normal\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic3.zhimg.com/50/v2-f9ecf0c3d8a913b92e538fbd91be90ce_hd.jpg\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"513\" data-original=\"https://pic4.zhimg.com/v2-f406e6b7c6499c2cc1f2783e1794cc59_r.jpg\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;513&#39; height=&#39;300&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"513\" data-rawheight=\"300\" data-size=\"normal\"